                <p class="m-0 text-center font-bold">🏆 駐車場対決の勝者は…<br>
                <span class="text-blue-600 text-lg">【ジャンボ】（ストレスフリー！）</span></p>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-10 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="bg-slate-800 text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm">5</span> 
